
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Happy Birthday 🎉</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin:0;
      font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f1021, #1b1e3c);
      color:#fff;
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    /* Confetti animation */
    .confetti {
      position:absolute;
      width:10px; height:10px;
      background: #ffd166;
      top:-10px;
      animation: fall linear infinite;
      opacity:0.9;
    }
    @keyframes fall {
      0% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg); }
      100% { transform: translateY(110vh) rotate(360deg); }
    }

    .wrap {
      min-height:100vh;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      padding:20px;
      position:relative;
      z-index:2;
    }
    .hero {
      background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      padding:30px;
      border-radius:20px;
      max-width:900px;
      display:grid;
      gap:20px;
      grid-template-columns:1fr 2fr;
      align-items:center;
    }
    @media(max-width:700px){ .hero{ grid-template-columns:1fr; text-align:center } }
    .btn {
      background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ffd166,#ffb703);
      border:none;
      padding:12px 20px;
      border-radius:14px;
      font-weight:600;
      cursor:pointer;
      margin-top:10px;
    }
    .image-box img { max-width:100%; border-radius:16px; }

    /* Modal */
    .modal {
      display:none;
      position:fixed;
      top:0; left:0;
      width:100%; height:100%;
      background:rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      z-index:200;
    }
    .modal-content {
      background:#fff;
      color:#000;
      padding:30px;
      border-radius:16px;
      text-align:center;
      max-width:500px;
      box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      animation: pop 0.5s ease;
    }
    @keyframes pop {
      from { transform:scale(0.5); opacity:0; }
      to { transform:scale(1); opacity:1; }
    }
    .close {
      float:right;
      font-size:24px;
      cursor:pointer;
      font-weight:bold;
      color:#333;
    }
    .modal-buttons {
      margin-top:20px;
      display:flex;
      justify-content:center;
      gap:15px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    /* Hidden video */
    #birthdayVideo {
      display:none;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Confetti Container -->
  <div id="confetti-container"></div>

  <!-- HOME PAGE -->
  <main class="wrap">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="image-box">
        <img src="k.jpeg" alt="Birthday image" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h1>Happy Birthday <span style="color:#ffd166">KEERTHANA</span> 🎂</h1>
        <p>Wishing you a day filled with smiles, surprises, and joy ✨</p>
        <button class="btn" id="openGreeting">Open Greeting 💌</button>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- GREETING MODAL 1 -->
  <div class="modal" id="greetingModal1">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <span class="close" id="closeGreeting1">&times;</span>
      <h2>🎉 Happy Birthday 🎉</h2>
      <p>Today is your special day, and I want you to know how much you mean to me. Life has given us countless memories together—some filled with laughter, some with tears, and all of them precious.

You have always been more than just my sister. You have been my friend, my guide, my partner in crime, and one of the most important people in my life. No matter how much we argue, tease each other, or go our separate ways, my heart always knows that you are one of my greatest blessings.

As we grow older, I realize how quickly time passes. 
<p>The days when we spent every moment together have become beautiful memories that I cherish deeply. Sometimes those memories make me smile, and sometimes they make me emotional because I know those moments can never come back exactly the same way.

On your birthday, I don't just wish for your happiness—I pray that every dream you hold close to your heart comes true. May your life be filled with endless joy, success, good health, and people who truly appreciate the wonderful person you are.</p>



</p>

      <div class="modal-buttons">
        <button class="btn" id="nextBtn">Next ➡️</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- GREETING MODAL 2 -->
  <div class="modal" id="greetingModal2">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <span class="close" id="closeGreeting2">&times;</span>
      <p>
          Happy Birthday, my sister. ❤️




        </p>
        <p>
         May your smile never fade, your heart never break, and your happiness never end.
        </p>
        <p>
         🎉 I love you and I am proud to call you my sister. 🎉
        </p>
        <p>Thank you for being my sister, for supporting me when I needed strength, and for making my life brighter just by being in it.

No matter where life takes us, you will always have a special place in my heart.</p>

      <div class="modal-buttons">
        <button class="btn" id="videoBtn">🎬 Play Video</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Hidden Video -->
  <video id="birthdayVideo" controls>
    <source src="sisv.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    Your browser does not support the video tag.
  </video>

  <script>
    // First Greeting modal
    const openBtn = document.getElementById("openGreeting");
    const modal1 = document.getElementById("greetingModal1");
    const closeBtn1 = document.getElementById("closeGreeting1");
    const nextBtn = document.getElementById("nextBtn");

    // Second modal
    const modal2 = document.getElementById("greetingModal2");
    const closeBtn2 = document.getElementById("closeGreeting2");
    const videoBtn = document.getElementById("videoBtn");
    const video = document.getElementById("birthdayVideo");

    openBtn.onclick = () => modal1.style.display = "flex";
    closeBtn1.onclick = () => modal1.style.display = "none";
    closeBtn2.onclick = () => modal2.style.display = "none";

    window.onclick = (e) => {
      if(e.target == modal1) modal1.style.display = "none";
      if(e.target == modal2) modal2.style.display = "none";
    };

    // Next button goes to second modal
    nextBtn.onclick = () => {
      modal1.style.display = "none";
      modal2.style.display = "flex";
    };

    // Video button action
    videoBtn.onclick = () => {
      video.style.display = "block";   // make sure it’s visible
      video.play();

      // Request fullscreen
      if (video.requestFullscreen) {
        video.requestFullscreen();
      } else if (video.webkitRequestFullscreen) { // Safari
        video.webkitRequestFullscreen();
      } else if (video.msRequestFullscreen) { // IE/Edge
        video.msRequestFullscreen();
      }
    };

    // Confetti generator
    function createConfetti(){
      const confetti = document.createElement("div");
      confetti.classList.add("confetti");
      document.getElementById("confetti-container").appendChild(confetti);

      confetti.style.left = Math.random()*100 + "vw";
      confetti.style.backgroundColor = ["#ff4d6d","#ffd166","#06d6a0","#118ab2","#ef476f"][Math.floor(Math.random()*5)];
      confetti.style.animationDuration = (Math.random()*3+2) + "s";

      setTimeout(()=>confetti.remove(), 5000);
    }
    setInterval(createConfetti, 150);
  </script>
</body>
</html>
